# DOS-UGANDA — source of truth

Synced `documents/` (Word, PDF, PPT) must comply with the Uganda call and **in-scope** official PDFs only. If anything conflicts, fix deliverables to match the official set. Also follow `.cursor/rules/documents.mdc` and `.cursor/rules/folder_structure.mdc`.

## Authority stack (Uganda scope)

1. [OFY summary](https://opportunitiesforyouth.org/2026/06/15/u-s-department-of-state-launches-up-to-60-million-funding-opportunity-to-strengthen-ugandas-health-system-through-the-health-foreign-assistance-mou-implementation-plan/) — public overview; not a substitute for PDFs.
2. `rules/opportunity-DFOP0017890-attachments/` — **use only:**
